{"type":"message","id":"e3a8ab05","parentId":"d9ee57b7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:54:54.976Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r369boyob0zi_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5078\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2757\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 095417 - The Phase 1 Advancement identifies TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) as the next critical experiment, but no TIC implementation exists yet. The pulse logs are available in `logs/` but need a classifier to extract invariants and measure prediction accuracy.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"calm-otter","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5078\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2757\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 095417 - The Phase 1 Advancement identifies TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) as the next critical experiment, but no TIC implementation exists yet. The pulse logs are available in `logs/` but need a classifier to extract invariants and measure prediction accuracy.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774360494974}}
{"type":"message","id":"697bbb7c","parentId":"e3a8ab05","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:54:54.978Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r369boyob0zi_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 095235\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: the (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me review the current state and what's needed next.\r\n\r\nLooking at the goals:\r\n1. Phase 0 COMPLETE - Sandbox foundation established\r\n2. Phase 1 COMPLETE - Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n3. Key insight: COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY - causal structure IS invariant structure\r\n\r\nThe NEXT ACTION is the TIC Experiment:\r\n- Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n- Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n- Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nI need to implement the Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) classifier. Let me look at what files exist and create the implementation.\r\n\r\nFirst, let me check the logs directory to understand the pulse log format, then implement the TIC classifier.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe next action is implementing the TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) classifier to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis. I need to analyze the pulse logs to classify invariant vs variant patterns and predict next-pulse content.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the TIC classifier script that analyzes pulse logs for invariant/variant patterns and measures classification accuracy + next-pulse prediction performance.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\r\n# Tests hypothesis: Causal structure = Invariant structure\r\n# Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$lookback = 20,  # Number of past pulses to analyze\r\n    [string]$logsDir = \"logs\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n\r\n# --- Phase 1: Load Pulse Logs ---\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Loading last $lookback pulse logs...\"\r\n\r\n$pulseFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path $logsDir -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | \r\n    Sort-Object Name -Descending | \r\n    Select-Object -First $lookback\r\n\r\nif ($pulseFiles.Count -lt 5) {\r\n    Write-Warning \"Insufficient pulse logs for analysis\"\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\n$pulses = @()\r\nforeach ($file in $pulseFiles) {\r\n    $content = Get-Content $file.FullName -Raw\r\n    $pulses += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        File = $file.Name\r\n        Timestamp = $file.LastWriteTime\r\n        Content = $content\r\n        WordCount = ($content -split '\\s+').Count\r\n        Lines = ($content -split \"`n\").Count\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Loaded $($pulses.Count) pulses\" -ForegroundColor Green\r\n\r\n# --- Phase 2: Extract Features for Invariant Detection ---\r\nWrite-Host \"`n=== Extracting Features ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\n\r\n# Define feature categories to track\r\n$featurePatterns = @{\r\n    \"Goals\" = \"(?i)(goal|phase|pending|completed)\"\r\n    \"Observations\" = \"(?i)observation\"\r\n    \"Actions\" = \"(?i)action|mutation|edit\"\r\n    \"Files\" = \"(?i)(?:file:|research/|logs/|state/)\"\r\n    \"Metrics\" = \"(?i)(?:accuracy|ratio|percentage|%)\"\r\n    \"Architecture\" = \"(?i)(?:architecture|temporal|attention|infant)\"\r\n    \"Causality\" = \"(?i)(?:causal|invariant|compression)\"\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Extract-Features {\r\n    param([string]$content)\r\n    \r\n    $features = @{}\r\n    foreach ($category in $featurePatterns.Keys) {\r\n        $pattern = $featurePatterns[$category]\r\n        $matches = [regex]::Matches($content, $pattern)\r\n        $features[$category] = $matches.Count\r\n    }\r\n    $features[\"TotalWords\"] = ($content -split '\\s+').Count\r\n    $features[\"TotalLines\"] = ($content -split \"`n\").Count\r\n    \r\n    return $features\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Extract features from all pulses\r\n$featureHistory = @()\r\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt $pulses.Count; $i++) {\r\n    $features = Extract-Features -content $pulses[$i].Content\r\n    $featureHistory += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        Index = $i\r\n        File = $pulses[$i].File\r\n        Features = $features\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# --- Phase 3: Invariant vs Variant Classification ---\r\nWrite-Host \"`n=== Invariant/Variant Classification ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\n\r\n# An invariant feature: stable across multiple consecutive pulses\r\n# A variant feature: changes frequently\r\n\r\n$invariantCriteria = @{\r\n    MinStableCount = 3  # Feature must appear in this many consecutive pulses\r\n    MaxVariance = 0.2   # Normalized variance must be below this\r\n}\r\n\r\n$classification = @()\r\n\r\nfor ($i = 1; $i -lt $featureHistory.Count; $i++) {\r\n    $prev = $featureHistory[$i-1].Features\r\n    $curr = $featureHistory[$i].Features\r\n    \r\n    $differences = @{}\r\n    $totalDiff = 0\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($key in $featurePatterns.Keys) {\r\n        $diff = [Math]::Abs($curr[$key] - $prev[$key])\r\n        $differences[$key] = $diff\r\n        $totalDiff += $diff\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Variant = changed significantly; Invariant = stayed same\r\n    $isInvariant = ($totalDiff -le 2)  # Threshold for \"significant change\"\r\n    \r\n    $classification += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        From = $featureHistory[$i-1].File\r\n        To = $featureHistory[$i].File\r\n        TotalDiff\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 09:53:09\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774360494976}}
